{"tid":2298653,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(圍爐post)外國讀書幾年，冇晒朋友，有冇可能去keep番？","createTime":"2020-11-24T07:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:36:22.000Z","uid":333681,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9837f564dadbf84679ce6b1f95e8f144c19de3c","tid":2298653,"uid":333681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"英國讀完書番黎香港3年， 有幾次試過約中學朋友見面， 好多時都話唔得閒， 攪攪下自己都冇咩心機， 冇再去維繫。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家間中諗起舊時回憶， 都幾開心， 仲有冇可能whatapp佢地約見面？係咪好遲啦？定係注定冇晒中學朋友。<br />\n<br />\n出左黎做野， 真係好難識朋友， 攪到社交圈子好細。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2483a8af88039ebb0c7462ba591505c5cc0b2e8e","tid":2298653,"uid":127095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed90f746c8f9163cdadc7dd0b754f02ea7280bd9","tid":2298653,"uid":333681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2483a8af88039ebb0c7462ba591505c5cc0b2e8e","tid":2298653,"uid":127095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"完全明白， 都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔太敢直接whatapp佢地， 好似好odd咁"},{"pid":"046a45e382b3905c6ece4ea660670410757602a6","tid":2298653,"uid":379493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"一樣 慶幸自己多興趣 平時都忙 先無咁無聊"},{"pid":"49935ab1a5906613db9da457f56dd89b5de74510","tid":2298653,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"我仲要係去外國嗰時未興whatsapp<br />\n番黎香港個個都whatsapp左成年，我先岩岩開&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416bd226ef01dc389cea55c